Derivation provenance
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

This module was derived from the KataGo cpp/search/analysisdata.h
and /cpp/search/searchresults.cpp source at upstream commit:

    4f78e16742c25ff7c78156a1aef9f1d00df6d5b0
    ("Fix clear_cache crash on analysis engine", 2026-01-06)

Local modifications added transposition tracking to the analysis
engine output. The MIT license terms apply to both the original
upstream code and the local modifications within this subdirectory.

To inspect the upstream code at the fork point:
    git -C <katago-checkout> show 4f78e16742c25ff7c78156a1aef9f1d00df6d5b0

